  "sn22.104": "The aggregates considered in light of the four noble truths in terms of suffering.",
  "sn22.105": "The aggregates considered in light of the four noble truths in terms of identity.",
  "sn22.106":
    "The aggregates are to be fully understood, ending the defilements is the full understanding of them, and an arahant is the one who has achieved this.",
